text: The Knox United Soccer Club is an Australian semi-professional soccer club based in the Melbourne suburb of Rowville, operating under license from Football Federation Victoria.http://websites.sportstg.com/club_info.cgi?c=1-8746-124260-0-0 Currently competing in the southern conference of Victorian State League Division 5,http://websites.sportstg.com/team_info.cgi?id=26155770&client;=1-8746-124260-0-0&compID;=514498&a;=LADDER the club was established by members of the Melbourne's Italian community in 2003.https://www.knoxunited.com/club-history Operating a junior academy and amateur team senior football since its inception, the club took to competitive state football for the 2018 Football Federation Victoria season finishing ninth in VSL 5 south.http://www.ozfootball.net/ark/Clubs/VIC/Vic_Active_K.html#KnoxUnited For the 2019 season, United finished 5th.http://www.ozfootball.net/ark/States/VIC/2019SD5ST.html ==References== Category:Soccer clubs in Melbourne Category:Soccer clubs in Victoria (Australia) Category:Association football clubs established in 2003 Category:Italian-Australian culture in Melbourne Category:Italian-Australian backed sports clubs of Victoria Category:Victorian State League teams Category:2003 establishments in Australia
